OL,6,FIn the video, recorded in July 2020,
OL,7,Fthe 42-year-old calls Klopp a "German
OL,8,F****" and "f***ing arrogant". He is
OL,9,Falso heard to say it had been "s***"
OL,10,Fto be fourth official at a Liverpool
OL,11,Fmatch in the summer of 2020.
OL,13,FCoote was suspended from his role,
OL,14,Fbefore he was sacked in December 2024.
OL,16,FHis misconduct was defined as an
OL,17,Faggravated breach under the FA's rules
OL,18,Fbecause there was a reference to
OL,19,FKlopp's nationality.
